rows.label: qev056501_MSG0001
rows.name:
People keep telling me I'm like a whole different person
lately. That I've gotten all hardworking and responsible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0002
rows.name: A while ago, this plant was attacked by cantors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0003
rows.name: Ever since, nobody's wanted to manage the place.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0004
rows.name: But I volunteered. I mean, SOMEONE had to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_JNK0010
rows.name: Ask about the Plant

rows.label: qev056501_SEL0011
rows.name: Inquire as to the plant's present condition.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_JNK0020
rows.name: Ask about Volunteering

rows.label: qev056501_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask why Rosie signed up for this job.

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0005
rows.name:
It's functioning well, and we have a steady supply of
mineral-rich water as a result.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0006
rows.name:
And the autosentries those Orphe built give us peace
of mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0007
rows.name:
...Although lately they've been acting a bit funny.
So I guess that's my one concern.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0008
rows.name:
They'll stop working, then suddenly start back up.
And sometimes they just move all...erratically.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0009
rows.name:
I guess to try to make up for what happened?
Or because I realized how toxic jealousy can be...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0010
rows.name:
I wanted to do something for other people, you know?
And this is really important work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0011
rows.name:
We have a steady supply of the clean, mineral-rich
water we need to live thanks to this plant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0012
rows.name:
And the autosentries those Orphe built give us peace
of mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0013
rows.name:
...Although lately they've been acting a bit funny.
So I guess that's my one concern.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0014
rows.name:
They'll stop working, then suddenly start back up.
And sometimes they just move all...erratically.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0015
rows.name:
An Orphean built the autosentries.
Guy named Tan'celeg, right?
And I hear that you helped out?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0016
rows.name:
If you wouldn't mind, could you head back to New LA
and grab him? I'd feel better if he gave those buckets
of bolts the once-over.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0017
rows.name: Thanks. I'll just be here working while you get him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0018
rows.name:
The city needs a lot of water, and I owe it to the
friends I lost to provide it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev056501_MSG0019
rows.name:
Would you bring Tan'celeg here from the city?
He's probably in his usual spot.[ST:wait ]
